trans-unit.source: Represents a COM class that is described in a manifest.
trans-unit.target: Représente une classe COM décrite dans le manifeste.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.Tasks.Deployment.ManifestUtilities.ComClass" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialise une nouvelle instance de la classe <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.Tasks.Deployment.ManifestUtilities.ComClass" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets the class identifier (ClsId) for a <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.Tasks.Deployment.ManifestUtilities.ComClass" /> object.
trans-unit.target: Obtient l’identificateur de classe (ClsId) pour un objet <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.Tasks.Deployment.ManifestUtilities.ComClass" />.

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.String" /> formatted in the pattern {xxxxxxxx-xxxx-xxxx-xxxx-xxxxxxxxxxxx}, where the value of the GUID is represented as a series of lower-case hexadecimal digits in groups of 8, 4, 4, 4, and 12 digits and separated by hyphens.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.String" /> mis en forme selon le modèle {xxxxxxxx-xxxx-xxxx-xxxx-xxxxxxxxxxxx}, où la valeur du GUID est représentée comme une série de chiffres hexadécimaux en minuscules par groupes de 8, 4, 4, 4 et 12 chiffres et séparés par des traits d’union.

trans-unit.source: An example of a return value is "{382c74c3-721d-4f34-80e5-57657b6cbc27}".
trans-unit.target: Exemple de valeur de retour : "{382c74c3-721d-4f34-80e5-57657b6cbc27}".

trans-unit.source: Gets the description of a <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.Tasks.Deployment.ManifestUtilities.ComClass" /> object.
trans-unit.target: Obtient la description d’un objet <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.Tasks.Deployment.ManifestUtilities.ComClass" />.

trans-unit.source: A description of the <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.Tasks.Deployment.ManifestUtilities.ComClass" /> object.
trans-unit.target: Description de l’objet <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.Tasks.Deployment.ManifestUtilities.ComClass" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets the programmatic identifier (ProgId) of a <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.Tasks.Deployment.ManifestUtilities.ComClass" /> object.
trans-unit.target: Obtient l'identificateur programmatique (ProgId) d'un objet <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.Tasks.Deployment.ManifestUtilities.ComClass" />.

trans-unit.source: The programmatic identifier of the <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.Tasks.Deployment.ManifestUtilities.ComClass" /> object.
trans-unit.target: Identificateur programmatique de l'objet <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.Tasks.Deployment.ManifestUtilities.ComClass" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets the threading model of a <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.Tasks.Deployment.ManifestUtilities.ComClass" /> object.
trans-unit.target: Obtient le modèle de thread d'un objet <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.Tasks.Deployment.ManifestUtilities.ComClass" />.

trans-unit.source: A string such as "Apartment".
trans-unit.target: Exemple de chaîne : "Appartement".

trans-unit.source: Gets a value that is the identifier of the type library that contains type information about the class.
trans-unit.target: Obtient une valeur qui est l’identificateur de la bibliothèque de types qui contient les informations de type sur la classe.

trans-unit.source: The identifier of the type library that contains type information about the class.
trans-unit.target: Identificateur de la bibliothèque de types qui contient les informations de type sur la classe.

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.String" /> formatted in the pattern {xxxxxxxx-xxxx-xxxx-xxxx-xxxxxxxxxxxx}, where the value of the GUID is represented as a series of lower-case hexadecimal digits in groups of 8, 4, 4, 4, and 12 digits and separated by hyphens.
